////                                                                   ////
//// This file is part of CCS's PIC USB driver code.  See USB.H        ////
//// for more documentation and a list of examples.                    ////
////                                                                   ////
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
////                                                                   ////
//// Version History:                                                  ////
////                                                                   ////
//// Oct 27th, 2011:                                                   ////
