////     send SERIAL_STATE messages in one packet.                     ////
////                                                                   ////
//// April 7th, 2009:                                                  ////
////   Vista 'code 10' issues resolved.                                ////
////                                                                   ////
////                                                                   ////
//// March 5th, 2009:                                                  ////
